  <brief_title>Clinical Assessment of the Use of the R8 Respiratory Rate Counter in Post-Operative Recovery in Adults and Adolescents</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Assessment of the Use of the R8 Respiratory Rate Counter in Post-Operative Recovery in Adults and Adolescents</official_title>
  <sponsors>
