  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to to establish whether or not measurement of respiratory rate taken using the
      Anaxsys Technology Ltd Respiratory Counter (R8 Counter) are equivalent to manual respiratory
      rate counting methods in patients receiving oxygen via a face mask.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
